Package: VACANT
Title: Variant Annotation Clustering AssociatioN Test
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Shu-Hsien", "Cho", email = "scho2@mdanderson.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A framework for rare variant association testing in biobank-scale
    data. Clusters rare variants into risk tiers using multi-dimensional
    annotation scores and a Pareto Staircase boundary, then performs aggregated
    association testing via Firth logistic regression and ACAT.
